                        <msContents>
                            <summary>
                                This is a famous, comment-text commentary on al-Taṣrīf al-ʿīzzá of al-Zanjānī (655 Qamarī) on Arabic Morphology (declension). Many commentaries have been written on this book, which are listed in Kashf al-Ẓunūn (2/1139). Taftāzānī completed this commentary in 738 Qamarī, 
                                at the age of 19, in his hometown, Faryūmad.
                            </summary>
